OL,3,CJim Clark Rally pays tribute to co
OL,4,Cdriver who died in last year's event
OL,6,FDrivers and organisers gathered ahead
OL,7,Fof Friday's ceremonial start in Duns
OL,8,Ftown centre to remember Welshman Dai
OL,9,FRoberts at this year's Jim Clark Rally.
OL,11,FA short speech was made detailing his
OL,12,Flove of rallying and his contribution
OL,13,Fto the sport, followed by a round of
OL,14,Fapplause.
OL,16,FMemorial stickers have also been
OL,17,Fplaced on every car to keep Dai's
OL,18,Fmemory at the heart of the event this
OL,19,Fweekend.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
