OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1779872675
OL,3,CJim Clark Rally pays tribute to co
OL,4,Cdriver who died in last year's event
OL,6,FThe British Rally Championship (BRC)
OL,7,Fsaid returning to the Jim Clark Rally
OL,8,Fwas "always going to be tough" for the
OL,9,Fmotorsport community but they hoped to
OL,10,F"make it a good one for Dai."
OL,12,F39-year-old Dai Roberts was killed
OL,13,Fwhen the car he was in crashed on the
OL,14,FEdrom Mains Road on Saturday 24 May
OL,15,F2025, during the closed road event
OL,16,Fheld annually around Duns in the
OL,17,FScottish Borders.
OL,19,FDriver James Williams was taken to
OL,20,Fhospital with serious injuries and has
OL,21,Fnot returned to compete this weekend.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
