PN,35703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1779872675
OL,3,CJim Clark Rally pays tribute to co
OL,4,Cdriver who died in last year's event
OL,6,FAs a mark of respect, the Edrom stage
OL,7,Fhas been removed this year.
OL,9,FNamed after Berwickshire farmer and
OL,10,Ftwo-time Formula One champion Jim
OL,11,FClark, the event has become a
OL,12,Fcornerstone of the British motorsport
OL,13,Fcalendar since it's inception in 1970.
OL,15,FAround 240 cars will be competing over
OL,16,Fthe two day event, with the Reivers
OL,17,FRally rounding off the weekend on
OL,18,FSunday.
OL,20,FThe BRC's statement ahead of the event
OL,21,Fread:
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1779872675
OL,3,CJim Clark Rally pays tribute to co
OL,4,Cdriver who died in last year's event
OL,6,F"This was always going to be tough.
OL,8,F"Heading back to the Jim Clark Rally
OL,9,Fthis weekend will be a difficult one
OL,10,Ffor many, for competitors, officials,
OL,11,Fvolunteers, supporters, and for all of
OL,12,Fus involved in the British Rally
OL,13,FChampionship.
OL,15,F"Just under 12 months ago, we lost one
OL,16,Fof the very best in Dai Roberts. A
OL,17,Fhugely respected and much-loved member
OL,18,Fof the BRC family, Dai's loss
OL,19,Fcontinues to be felt deeply across the
OL,20,Fchampionship and the wider rallying
OL,21,Fcommunity.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1779872675
OL,3,CJim Clark Rally pays tribute to co
OL,4,Cdriver who died in last year's event
OL,6,F"Dai was an integral part of the
OL,7,Fseries, admired not only for his
OL,8,Ftalent and professionalism, but for
OL,9,Fthe warmth, humour and friendship he
OL,10,Fbrought to every event and everyone
OL,11,Faround him.
OL,13,F"Returning to the Jim Clark Rally is
OL,14,Fnot easy, and there will undoubtedly
OL,15,Fbe emotional moments throughout the
OL,16,Fweekend, but we know Dai's passion for
OL,17,Frallying and for the championship
OL,18,Fnever wavered.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1779872675
OL,3,CJim Clark Rally pays tribute to co
OL,4,Cdriver who died in last year's event
OL,6,F"More than anything, we are sure he
OL,7,Fwould have wanted the rally to
OL,8,Fcontinue, and for the BRC family to
OL,9,Fcome together once again in the spirit
OL,10,Fof the sport he loved so much.
OL,12,F"We send our heartfelt thoughts to
OL,13,FLouise, Mike and all of the Roberts
OL,14,Ffamily at this time, as well as to
OL,15,FDai's friends, team-mates and everyone
OL,16,Fwho had the privilege of knowing him.
OL,17,FOur thoughts also extend to James
OL,18,FWilliams at this difficult time.
OL,20,F"Let's make this a good one for Dai."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
